<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../218/700218.xml">
DirectShow</link></hypothesis>
</concept>
</idea>
</model>
 SDK is required to build some <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../797/52797.xml">
camera</link> input-related parts of OpenCV on Windows. This SDK is found in the <it>Samples\Multimedia\DirectShow\BaseClasses</it> subdirectory of the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../733/2671733.xml">
Microsoft Platform SDK</link>, which must be built prior to the building of OpenCV.</p>

